# Komodachi Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Prisma ORM
- PostgreSQL
- ElevenLabs Conversational AI

## Code Style
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer server components unless interactivity is needed
- Use 'use client' directive when necessary
- Follow TypeScript strict mode
- Use Tailwind classes for styling

## File Structure
- `/app` - Next.js app router pages and layouts
- `/components` - Reusable React components
- `/lib` - Utility functions and shared code
- `/prisma` - Database schema and migrations

## Color Palette
- Primary: #0378A6
- Primary Light: #6AB9D9
- Accent: #F2B705
- Accent Dark: #D9910B
- Accent Darker: #BF7D2C

## API Routes
- Follow RESTful conventions
- Use proper HTTP methods
- Return consistent JSON responses
- Handle errors gracefully

## Database
- Use Prisma for all database operations
- Follow the schema in prisma/schema.prisma
- Use transactions for complex operations

## ElevenLabs Integration
- All voice AI logic in lib/elevenlabs-config.ts
- Webhook handlers in app/api/elevenlabs/
- System prompts in Indonesian language

